1.5
log
@OpenBSD does not support AI_ADDRCONFIG so SpamAssassin did not use
getaddrinfo.  This caused a lot of warnings and the regression tests
failed.  Remove the check for AI_ADDRCONFIG from the eval that
imports Socket.pm.
OK sthen@@
